title: Urbanization in Iran 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: Overall Share of urban population in total population has increased over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Share of urban population in total population, of value 74.9 was reached at Year 2018
Minimum Share of urban population in total population about 72.83 was reached at Year 2014
min_summary: In general Share of urban population in total population has stayed the same over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2018.
